author: ajaquith
msg: Preview is now a tab, and its contents refresh automatically when it is clicked based on the editor's contents. This replaces "live" or "sneak" preview. It looks good and works well. Related: a new EventResolution class now exists to help events methods return AJAX that stripes-support.js understands.

author: ajaquith
msg: TabbedSectionTag gains an onclick() attribute that passes contents through to the underlying <div>. This feature is super-useful and enables the new preview functionality. Refactored TabTag to make it simpler.
